    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 MRL 2 requirements. Validation comparison demonstrates CFD model predicts NIH within 15% of experimental measurements across all 5 operating points. RH < 1 acceptance criterion satisfied. An uncertainty quantification campaign was completed and results are documented in the validation report; parametric sensitivity rankings confirm the model is not unduly sensitive to input perturbations within the clinical operating envelope. The credibility evidence package supports regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device hemolysis assessment.",
